  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/449160/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1772963184\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/449160/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1772963184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/449160/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1772963184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Land it Rocket</strong> is a challenging yet accessible 2D rocket-landing game inspired by classic lunar landers.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skills across <strong>28 carefully crafted levels</strong>, navigating narrow passages, avoiding hazards, and perfecting your landing technique.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're chasing high scores or just want to relax and land safely, there's a mode for you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🚀 28 handcrafted levels with increasing difficulty  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🌌 Endless Mode for unlimited challenge  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🎮 Full controller support – plug and play  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- ✨ Simple controls, clean visuals, smooth performance  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for fans of physics-based platformers, retro challenges, and relaxing gameplay loops.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Land it Rocket</strong> is a challenging yet accessible 2D rocket-landing game inspired by classic lunar landers.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skills across <strong>28 carefully crafted levels</strong>, navigating narrow passages, avoiding hazards, and perfecting your landing technique.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're chasing high scores or just want to relax and land safely, there's a mode for you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🚀 28 handcrafted levels with increasing difficulty  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🌌 Endless Mode for unlimited challenge  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🎮 Full controller support – plug and play  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- ✨ Simple controls, clean visuals, smooth performance  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for fans of physics-based platformers, retro challenges, and relaxing gameplay loops.</p>",
